            <h2>Vote.gov</h2>
            <p>Vote.gov makes it easier for eligible voters to participate in our democratic process by providing
                streamlined information on how to vote. Visitors can register electronically in states that allow it,
                and download a printable application in multiple languages for those states where electronic
                registration isn't an option. Vote.gov was ranked as the <a
                        href="{{ '/assets/documents/2017-benchmarking-us-government-websites.pdf' | url }}">#1 federal
                    website in 2017</a> by the Information Technology &amp; Innovation Foundation for meeting basic
                standards in security, speed, mobile friendliness, and accessibility.</p>
