            <h2>FedRAMP</h2>
            <p>The Federal Risk and Authorization Management Program (FedRAMP) is a government-wide program that
                provides a standardized approach to security assessment, authorization, and continuous monitoring for
                cloud products and services. FedRAMP's choice to use Pages for its main website speaks to the security
                and reliability of the Pages infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
